If it's your first time running the project, create a virtual environment:
python3 -m venv chatbot_venv

For your first time and every time you want to run the project, start your virtual environment 
by navigating to the backend directory in your terminal and running: 
source chatbot_venv/bin/activate

If it's your first time running the project, also run:
pip install fastapi uvicorn openai python-dotenv

Then to, finishing starting up the backend, run:
uvicorn main:app --reload

To set up the frontend, navigate to the frontend directory in your terminal and run:
open index.html